platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Fall in love with a new book

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Inspired by the timeless story of a little egg on a leaf, Hungry Caterpillar Play School is as sweet and colorful as Eric Carles beloved childrens book. The app is all about play and exploration; kids can draw, color, sing, and even learn to grow strawberries (for the caterpillars snack).
As sweet and colourful as the beloved childrens book, kids can draw, colour, sing and even learn to grow strawberries for the caterpillars snack!
